review:
1) First use of app. Created Mobile Order at home and completed order on arrival. Order number appeared on customer service display. Finding our order on their screen, staff informed us ice cream machine was not working so could not provide sundaes. Staff had no knowledge of how to cancel an order in the app, so provided refund directly to card. Later discovered we did not receive a full refund. 
2) Next day, 2nd use of app. Same process for sundaes, learned ice cream machine was still inoperative. The order was canceled within the app. Items were removed from the order, with no items and no charge showing in the app. Later discovered two other items were subsequently charged by the app, even though neither was in the order and neither was selected. 
App needs some improvements:
1) having selected a store, if a product is not available it should not be possible to order it;
2) it should be user friendly and easier to cancel an item or order;
3) quality control - it should not be possible for the app to charge for items not ordered;
4) some offers are only available with a printed receipt, which don‚Äôt appear possible using the app;
5) app should provide for additional written comments for special needs or requests.
